Phase 1:
    Can read most standard image formats
    Can display images in some unix-like terminal emulators

Phase 2:
    Can read nearly all common image formats
    Image printing detail can be specified
    Add more unix-like terminal emulator support

Phase 3:
    All (or as many as possible) unix-like terminal emulators supported
    Automatically choose best display method for the unix-like terminal emulator used
    Start work on support for Windows command prompt [optional]
    
Phase 4:
    Fully support Windows command prompt [optional]
